OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells for many, with the
OL,6,Frisk of some showers moving north and
OL,7,Feastwards. Feeling warm in the
OL,8,Fsunshine, though a touch cooler along
OL,9,Fthe east coast. Some low cloud and
OL,10,Fcoastal fog developing across
OL,11,Fsouthwest England.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud amounts increasing
OL,14,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,15,Fshowery rain in the north and west at
OL,16,Ftimes. Mostly dry in the southeast,
OL,17,Fwith clear spells. Winds staying light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
