OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FOften cloudy in the north and
OL,6,Fwest, with patchy rain. Rain turning
OL,7,Fheavy through the evening. Drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter elsewhere, with the best of
OL,9,Fthe warm sunshine across southeast
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
